data.description: This is an amazing house in a sought-after neighborhood on a dead-end street! This 4 bed, 2 full bath home is surrounded by woods has been well maintained over the years! The front welcomes you into an open foyer with beautiful hardwood flooring throughout. The living room offers plenty of space for the family and carpet. The living room opens into a family room with a stunning gas fireplace with custom built ins and a dining room area. There's a back door access into a 3 seasons room overlooking the park like setting backyard and hardwoods. The kitchen offers plenty of solid wood cabinetry, laminate countertops, tile flooring, stainless appliances and an island. The primary suite is located on the first floor with a walk-in closet and an updated full bathroom with a walk-in shower, newer vanity and tile flooring. There is access to the bathroom into the kitchen as well. Upstairs hosts a large open area that would be ideal for another living space and a playroom. 3 bedrooms on the second floor with plenty of closet space in each and carpet. A full bathroom with a double vanity and tub surround. The basement has plenty of space for storage, the laundry area and an extra room. Hi-efficiency furnace/AC. 150-amp panel. 40 Gallon HWT. New glass block windows. Newer Dimensional shingled roof. Vinyl siding. Attached 2 car garage with nature stone and new door openers. Lakeview School District. Schedule an appointment today!!
